    "body": "as a side issue:\n\nWe should not accept a pure string in the categorical constructor only list-likes.\n\n```\nIn [3]: pd.Categorical('foo')\nOut[3]:\n[foo]\nCategories (1, object): [foo]\n\nIn [4]: pd.Categorical('foo', 'bar')\nOut[4]:\n[NaN]\nCategories (1, object): [bar]\n```\n\nshould prob raise an issue.\n"
